{"tid":2366321,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"運動員今井夢露退役拍AV 人生坎坷認患精神病","createTime":"2021-01-14T11:48:24.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-15T09:57:23.000Z","uid":16659,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"983218551410e904fb24b37b8922046ecf194fce","tid":2366321,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T11:48:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/l7_Ilg4mxr5LZKjORhhoNkHlx4w=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/P5IA55UQEFBEJKLDW4XA6IVITY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fl7_Ilg4mxr5LZKjORhhoNkHlx4w%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FP5IA55UQEFBEJKLDW4XA6IVITY.jpg&h=2d5d5000&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n33歲日本前滑雪板選手今井夢露，今日在個人網誌上自爆患上躁鬱症，多年來一直受到病情影響，出現失眠、抑鬱等問題，要長期接受治療，但她經歷過痛苦後，現在已考慮到如何面對周圍的人，令她已感覺好過得多，並勇敢地向外談到自己的情。<br />\n<br />\n今井夢露昔日是滑雪板天才少女，14歲奪得全國冠軍，18歲參加2006冬季奧運，可惜卻在預賽中跌倒淘汰，辜負日本國民期待，亦導致她的心靈受創，人生亦急轉直下，曾經沉迷幫襯鴨店，又當過夜場小姐及拍攝AV，還有自殺不遂、整容、離婚及流產等，種種原因令她患成了精神病患者。<br />\n<br />\n今井夢露所患的躁鬱症，亦稱雙極性情感性精神病、情緒兩極症，是精神病一種，經歷情緒的亢奮期和抑鬱期，躁鬱症也常伴隨焦慮症以及濫藥等心理問題。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/f9zncizGan24EvLNvcNJw1SDOcc=/802x811/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ZEPECKFBOJCQXM6PZUXH5TS3NU.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Ff9zncizGan24EvLNvcNJw1SDOcc%3D%2F802x811%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FZEPECKFBOJCQXM6PZUXH5TS3NU.JPG&h=451b7a11&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/1GbpY5JLKEbEW7J7wiLF_7DSAKc=/802x839/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/SIOR3UJEVFB25CKPH3R7Z5JI4I.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F1GbpY5JLKEbEW7J7wiLF_7DSAKc%3D%2F802x839%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FSIOR3UJEVFB25CKPH3R7Z5JI4I.JPG&h=87342aea&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b05bb712ece660928f3c0df3141089e6f82fe930","tid":2366321,"uid":33437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T11:49:36.000Z","msg":"可惜<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53f7da30185380863484ec4f8a383a6f34496d3f","tid":2366321,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T11:55:28.000Z","msg":"曾經沉迷幫襯鴨店<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/potion.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/potion.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e8818c97f8918465c2389c37f1a87c73bfdf951","tid":2366321,"uid":34241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T14:53:12.000Z","msg":"係咪膝頭哥黎"},{"pid":"09e021af3a331ef4ce2b6f8a97baf4241212b929","tid":2366321,"uid":57572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T03:47:26.000Z","msg":"假波 不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50b8daa123ef54769710d0acbeec6afb86af52b4","tid":2366321,"uid":18012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T03:48:54.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"a8b1349a880d10ebb40d984e0cbf4e71085476a0","tid":2366321,"uid":83328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T03:52:18.000Z","msg":"唔知乜水<br />\n但樣衰都咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db48d9b624c89927d7e8d0931fb357480451e9cf","tid":2366321,"uid":203797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a8b1349a880d10ebb40d984e0cbf4e71085476a0","tid":2366321,"uid":83328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T03:52:18.000Z","msg":"唔知乜水<br />\n但樣衰都咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T09:57:23.000Z","msg":"仲整過容..."}]}